’ђђЪяTitle: This week in Nu #60
Path: This week in Nu #60
Content:
Couchbase announced a 
[link: http://couchbase.sh] new shell based on Nushell
andrasio simplified 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2674] making column paths
, added a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2670] ``flatten``
 command
, made sure that 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2667] chart command binaries are properly installed
, updated the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2666] wix plugin checker
, added back 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2662] bigint/bigdecimal serialization
gillespiecd fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2669] typo in a crate description
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2658] tests for get_data_by_key
, cleaned up 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2654] some extra files in the root
fdncred added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2668] bson and sqlite to the wix
jonathandturenr released 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2663] version 0.21
andrasio/fdncred worked on an 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2661] xpath plugin
 (see 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2656] also
)
wcarss disabled 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2659] rustyline's bracketed paste
RedlineTriad fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2655] some string concatenation logic
luccasmmg added a new 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2650] ``format filesize``
 command for formatting filesizes
jonstodle updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/62] command docs on the website to 0.20
mbeijen fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/book/pull/133] a typo in the book
